00 GHz, with the maximum\npossible T_B scaling roughly as 1/frequency. Less massive relativistic jet\nsources, such as microquasars, are even better candidates for producing\ncyclotron maser emission, primarily in the infrared and optical bands.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2005 22:51:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
